    • Method Detail

      • listen

        void listen(java.lang.Object other)
        Listen for changes in a reference. A reference can be a single Cell or several cells in a Range. For every cell in a Range, this Cell subscribes as listener, and the other cell is appended to the references Vector for this Cell.
        Parameters:
        other - Another Cell instance, or Range containing cells.
